  // === AUTO-GENERATED FROM UCSC CATALOG (do not hand-edit below) ===
  // 2064 courses auto-merged from UCSC General Catalog
  // Re-run scripts/fetch_ucsc_courses.py + merge_into_courses_js.py to refresh.
  // Each entry has section=["FREE"] by default — edit manually if it
