    desc: "Special topics. Format varies each quarter. Prerequisite(s): PHIL 9 ; and two from PHIL 100A , PHIL 100B , and PHIL 100C . Enrollment restricted to senior philosophy majors and by permission of the instructor.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
  },
  "PHIL 195A": {
