    desc: "Examines the exploitation of African people as slaves throughout European colonies in the Americas. How did slavery affect slaves, enslavers, and their societies? Emphasizes the diversity of slave regimes and their importance for shaping American life for all.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
  },
  "HIS 116A": {
