    desc: "Explores the history of the Cold War from a global, multinational perspective. Begins with the opening salvos between the United States and the Soviet Union in 1945, and concludes with the collapse of the latter empire in 1991.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
  },
  "HIS 118A": {
