    units: 5, division: "upper",
    prereqs: [],
    ge: "PE-H", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Explores the history of a principal obsession of our age: the conspiracy. Focuses on the people who love them most: conspiracy theorists. Millions of people around the world believe in conspiracy theories. Why?",
