    desc: "A survey course on the social history of the Mexican (Chicana/o) community and people in the U.S. through the 20th century. Themes include resistance, migration, labor, urbanization, culture and politics.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
  },
  "HIS 130": {
