    prereqs: [],
    ge: "CC", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Examines the literary production of slave societies by looking at the literatures of several pre-modern slave societies; also develops a cultural-historical narrative that explains the origins of genocidal forms of plantation slavery in the Americas by tracing their origins back to Greece and Rome.",
