    ge: "CC", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "The Korean War has the dubious distinction of being known as the Forgotten War in a U.S. context. Course examines novels, short stories, film, popular visual narratives, and historical accounts of the Korean War and its often-circuitous legacies.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
