    prereqs: [],
    ge: null, quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Speaking, reading, and writing proficiency in Spanish required. A critical study of several representative texts from the early period of Spanish literature in their sociohistorical context. Included among the readings are El Poema del Cid, the Romancero, La Celestina, Lazarillo de Tormes, and a Golden Age play. Critical approach designations: Geographies, Histories. Distribution requirements: Poetry, Pre-1750.",
